docs.text: kilroyweb 🔗 kilroy web ui 📉 Overview 🔗 kilroyweb is a web ui for kilroy . It is a Next.js app that uses Mantine for styling. Running 🔗 With npm and node installed, run: npm install npm run start The app will be available at http://localhost:14000 .
